    <stitle>10 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS SPICER - DISASSEMBLE - INPUT SHAFT</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="disassemble" graphiccount="1">
        <title>INPUT SHAFT</title>
        <para>To disassemble the input shaft assembly, remove the snap ring (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f1302362">Figure 62</hotlnk>). Press the bearing off the shaft.
        </para>
        <figure id="f1302362" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1302362" filename="../figg13/G1302362.webp" type="webp"/>
            <caption>Figure 62. Input Shaft Disassembly</caption>
        </figure>
        <specpara>
            <warning>
                <para>When pressing bearings, use a shield to protect people from possible flying parts.</para>
            </warning>
        </specpara>
    </svcproc>
